trino-query-ui
--------------
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The following assets under packages/web/src/trino-lang/ are forked from the
trino-query-ui project (which itself derives its grammar from Trino, also
Apache-2.0):

  - SqlBase.g4                          (Trino SQL grammar)
  - generated/SqlBaseLexer.ts           (antlr4ng-generated lexer)
  - generated/SqlBaseParser.ts          (antlr4ng-generated parser)
  - generated/SqlBaseListener.ts        (antlr4ng-generated listener)
  - generated/SqlBaseVisitor.ts         (antlr4ng-generated visitor)
  - sql/TokenMap.ts                     (token-type → highlight-scope map)
  - sql/SqlBaseErrorListener.ts         (syntax-error collector)
  - sql/NamedQuery.ts                   (CTE / aliased-relation descriptor)
  - sql/StatementDescriptor.ts          (per-statement table reference)
  - sql/SqlBaseListenerImpl.ts          (decoration / table-reference listener; adapted)
  - sql/SpecialHighlight.ts             (table-name decoration; adapted)
  - schema/Catalog.ts, Schema.ts, Table.ts, Column.ts, TableReference.ts
                                        (metadata value objects; decoupled from
                                         the singleton SchemaProvider during fork)

Each forked source file carries an inline provenance comment at its head.

A copy of the Apache License, Version 2.0 may be obtained at:
  http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Modifications by the hubble project:
  - The original singleton `SchemaProvider` (which issued queries directly
    against Trino) was removed. Metadata is now supplied through a dependency-
    injected `MetadataSource` interface (see packages/web/src/trino-lang/sql/).
  - `QueryEditorPane` (a 950-line React monolith) was NOT forked; its editor
    behaviour was re-implemented as discrete Monaco providers under
    packages/web/src/editor/.
